离开 NBC 后，奥布莱恩开通[[Twitter|Twitter]]帐号，用来探索新的喜剧媒介。2010年3月11日，奥布莱恩在Twitter上宣布，开启名为《法律禁止在电视上玩幽默》的30城现场巡演<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2010/03/11/entertainment/main6289101.shtml |title=Conan O'Brien Announces Live Tour |publisher=CBS News |accessdate=2010-11-27 |date=2010-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100415062650/http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2010/03/11/entertainment/main6289101.shtml |archive-date=2010-04-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。消息公布数小时后，数个地点的门票售罄，为满足需求又加开场次。巡演于2010年4月12日在[[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]][[尤金_(俄勒冈州)|尤金市]]开始，2010年6月14日在[[佐治亚州|佐治亚州]][[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]结束<ref name="vansun">{{cite web|url=http://www.vancouversun.com/opinion/Vancouver+fans+crazy+Conan/2904329/story.html|first=Graeme|last=McRanor|title=Vancouver Fans Go Crazy for Conan|date=2010-04-14|accessdate=2010-04-15|publisher=Vancouver Sun}}{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，用上了《深夜秀》和《今夜秀》的诸多元素，其中包括视频剪辑、相声表演和客串登场名人。奥布莱恩开玩笑称因受到NBC的法律限制，为了避免官司，要把“自我取悦的熊猫”改名为“[[自慰|自慰]]的熊猫”<ref name="rollingstone-review">{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/culture/news/conan-obrien-revives-edgy-late-night-vibe-at-first-live-show-20100413|first=Scott|last=Sepich|title=Conan O'Brien Revives Edgy 'Late Night' Vibe at First Live Show|date=2010-04-13|accessdate=2011-01-24|publisher=滚石|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120831061356/http://www.rollingstone.com/culture/news/conan-obrien-revives-edgy-late-night-vibe-at-first-live-show-20100413|archive-date=2012-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。音乐贯穿了整场演出，包括热门迪斯科单曲《[[I_Will_Survive|我会活下去]]》和《重踏征途》（On the Road Again）<ref name="rollingstone-review"/>。喜剧演员[[雷吉·瓦特|雷吉·瓦特]]为奥布莱恩的巡演作开场表演<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nymag.com/arts/comics/profiles/66280/ |title=How Comedian Reggie Watts Has Become a National Phenomenon |publisher=New York Magazine |date=2010-05-30 |accessdate=2010-11-28 |last=Anderson |first=Sam |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100605040406/http://nymag.com/arts/comics/profiles/66280/ |archive-date=2010-06-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 移师TBS ===
[[File:Conan_O'Brien_speaking_at_TBS_rally.jpg|right]]的TBS电视台总部的集会支持者会面]]
巡演启动前不久，奥布莱恩宣布与有线电视台[[TBS|TBS]]签署协议，从2011年11月起，主持一档深夜品牌脱口秀节目。协议被公布前，奥布莱恩对此举持保留态度。一旦成行，喜剧演员[[乔治·洛佩兹|乔治·洛佩兹]]的节目《[[洛佩兹今夜秀|洛佩兹今夜秀]]》就要延迟至午夜播出。NBC想要让柯南学洛佩兹的有效方式。然而，洛佩兹据说奥布莱恩和这一举措感到兴奋<ref name="conantbs">{{cite news|url=http://mediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/04/12/how-the-conan-obrien-tbs-deal-happened/?src=busln|first=Bill|last=Carter|title=How the Conan O’Brien-TBS Deal Happened|date=2010-04-12|accessdate=2010-04-12|publisher=纽约时报|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100416151318/http://mediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/04/12/how-the-conan-obrien-tbs-deal-happened/?src=busln|archive-date=2010-04-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。洛佩兹随后表态，“我想不出有什么比得上柯南来引入我的节目......这是深夜喜剧新时代的开始<ref name="turner-picks">{{cite web | url = http://news.turner.com/article_display.cfm?article_id=5075 | title = Conan Picks a Home – And It’s TBS | date = 2010-04-12 | accessdate = 2010-11-08 | publisher = Turner Newsroom | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100417044214/http://news.turner.com/article_display.cfm?article_id=5075 | archive-date = 2010-04-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref> 。”特纳广播公司在官方新闻稿表示，跟奥布莱恩才谈判了一个星期，就正式宣布节目<ref name="turner-picks"/>。特纳娱乐网络公司总裁史蒂夫·库宁评论该公告称，“柯南一直是一代人的喜剧之音。TBS有着年轻喜剧爱好者的庞大观众群体，柯南的节目无疑会给这些粉丝更多观看我们电视的理由<ref name="turner-picks"/>。”

在这笔交易的声明中，奥布莱恩表示：“这三个月，我经历了从网络电视台到Twitter再到剧院现场演员，现在我要去有线电视台了。我的计划是完美的工作<ref name="turner-picks"/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://mediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/04/12/conan-obrien-will-do-a-late-night-show-on-tbs/ |title=Conan O’Brien Will Do a Late-Night Show on TBS |publisher=The New York Times |last=Carter |first=Bill |accessdate=2010-07-12 |date=2010-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100418062635/http://mediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/04/12/conan-obrien-will-do-a-late-night-show-on-tbs/ |archive-date=2010-04-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”奥布莱恩的制作公司Conaco，据称拥有所有演出的权利<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/04/conan-obrien-makes-tbs-deal/ |title=Conan O'Brien makes TBS deal! How it all went down, and how Team Conan thought out of the network box all along |last=Finke |first=Nikki |publisher=Deadline |accessdate=2010-04-12 |date=2010-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100414192053/http://www.deadline.com/2010/04/conan-obrien-makes-tbs-deal/ |archive-date=2010-04-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。除节目公告，TBS还制作了一小时特别节目，请来《柯南秀》的编剧，及参与奥布莱恩巡演的喜剧演员雷吉瓦<ref name="tbsspecial">{{cite web |url=http://news.turner.com/article_display.cfm?article_id=5177 |title=Andy Richter and Conan O’Brien Writers Team Up for One-Hour TBS Special |publisher=Turner Newsroom |date=2010-05-26 |accessdate=2010-11-11 |archive-date=2020-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117205250/https://pressroom.warnermedia.com/us |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该节目于2010年6月27日，而《柯南秀》直到11月初才开播<ref name="tbsspecial"/>。此外，在节目准备方面，全天候的“直通柯南秀”于2010年10月20日成立<ref name="cococam">{{cite web |url=http://news.turner.com/article_display.cfm?article_id=5414 |title="Live Coco Cam" Gives Conan O'Brien Fans Live 24-Hour Peephole into Team Coco Offices on Wednesday, Oct. 20 at 10 a.m. PT / 1 p.m. ET |publisher=Turner Newsroom |accessdate=2010-11-14 |date=2010-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724212004/http://news.turner.com/article_display.cfm?article_id=5414 |archive-date=2011-07-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，“LaBamba”里奇·罗森博格等《柯南秀》一众主创亮相<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nbclosangeles.com/entertainment/celebrity/NATL-Conan-Launches-24-Hour-Live-Coco-Cam-Online-105393298.html |title=Conan Launches 24-Hour Live "Coco Cam" |publisher=NBC News |last=Macht |first=Dan |accessdate=2010-11-14 |date=2010-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318084647/http://www.nbclosangeles.com/entertainment/celebrity/NATL-Conan-Launches-24-Hour-Live-Coco-Cam-Online-105393298.html |archive-date=2012-03-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年11月1日，播出奥布莱恩办公室的简短在线直播“零距离”。除了奥布莱恩、现场乐队成员杰里·维维诺和安迪·里希特担任主持人。有几位嘉宾主持了该节目，包括演员[[吉姆·帕森斯|吉姆·帕森斯]]和独立摇滚乐队[[钢铁火车|钢铁火车]]，共持续4分钟51秒<ref>{{cite web |url=http://watching-tv.ew.com/2010/11/01/conan-obrien-show-zero-online/ |title=Conan O'Brien online 'Show Zero' review: Gee, that was fast... |last=Tucker |first=Ken |publisher=Entertainment Weekly |date=2010-11-01 |accessdate=2010-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101105043831/http://watching-tv.ew.com/2010/11/01/conan-obrien-show-zero-online/ |archive-date=2010-11-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

开播前两周，一艘橙色的《柯南秀》飞艇进一步宣传节目<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boingboing.net/2010/10/12/the-birth-of-the-con.html |title=The Birth of the Conan Blimp |last=Barol |first=Bill |publisher=Boing Boing |date=2010-10-12 |accessdate=2010-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101201094657/http://boingboing.net/2010/10/12/the-birth-of-the-con.html |archive-date=2010-12-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。亚特兰大蓝天事务所设计曾于2010年[[美国职棒大联盟|美国职棒大联盟]]季后赛上，为TBS提供空中飞艇镜头。该飞艇已纳入《柯南秀》草图，包括插科打诨时，加里·布斯伴随飞艇在南加州出现，让柯南懊恼不已<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/video/item/conan-stalks-gary-busey|title=Conan Blimp Stalks Gary Busey|publisher=The Daily Beast|date=2010-11-23|accessdate=2010-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101125195605/http://www.thedailybeast.com/video/item/conan-stalks-gary-busey/|archive-date=2010-11-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 首播 ===
首期《柯南秀》“咩咩敲诈”<ref name="timefirst"/>，于美国东部时间2011年11月8日晚上11点开播<ref name="hpcar">{{cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2010/10/15/conan-drives-car-off-cliff_n_764335.html |title=Conan Drives Explosives-Filled Car Off Cliff In Amazing New TBS Promo |publisher=Huffington Post |accessdate=2010-10-22 |date=2010-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101018071519/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2010/10/15/conan-drives-car-off-cliff_n_764335.html |archive-date=2010-10-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。首位嘉宾是[[华盛顿州|华盛顿州]][[莱温芙丝镇_(华盛顿州)|莱温芙丝镇]]胡桃夹子博物馆馆长阿琳·瓦格纳<ref name="khq">{{cite web |url=http://www.khq.com/Global/story.asp?S=13465962 |title=Conan's New Show Debuts Tonight With Woman From Leavenworth As His First Guest |publisher=KHQ News |accessdate=2010-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120307171344/http://www.khq.com/Global/story.asp?S=13465962 |archive-date=2012-03-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="seattlest">{{cite web |url=http://seattlest.com/2010/11/08/cracking_nuts_arlene_wagner_to_be_c.php |title=Cracking Nuts: Washington's Arlene Wagner To Be Conan's First Guest |publisher=Seattlest |accessdate=2010-11-09 |date=2010-11-08 |last=Corsiglia |first=Gina |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101109192415/http://seattlest.com/2010/11/08/cracking_nuts_arlene_wagner_to_be_c.php |archive-date=2010-11-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。透过奥布莱恩官网TeamCoco.com上的粉丝民意调查，瓦格纳被选为首位嘉宾。其他候选者包括罗马教皇[[本笃十六世|本笃十六世]]、[[俄罗斯总统|俄罗斯总统]][[弗拉基米尔·普京|弗拉基米尔·普京]]、表演者[[贾斯丁·比伯|贾斯丁·比伯]]和[[Lady_Gaga|Lady Gaga]]及演员[[杰克·尼尔科森|杰克·尼尔科森]]等<ref name="seattlest" />。瓦格纳短暂露面后，喜剧演员[[塞斯·罗根|塞斯·罗根]]和女演员[[丽亚·米雪儿|丽亚·米雪儿]]登场，接着[[杰克·怀特|杰克·怀特]]表演歌曲《Twenty Flight Rock》<ref name="timefirst">{{cite web |url=http://tunedin.blogs.time.com/2010/11/09/conan-returns-stop-me-if-youve-heard-this-one-before/ |title=Conan Returns: Stop Me If You've Heard This One Before |publisher=Time |accessdate=2010-11-09 |date=2010-11-09 |last=Poniewozik |first=James |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101111113041/http://tunedin.blogs.time.com/2010/11/09/conan-returns-stop-me-if-youve-heard-this-one-before/ |archive-date=2010-11-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="firstweek">{{cite web|url=http://news.turner.com/article_display.cfm?article_id=5425|title=Conan O’Brien Announces First Week of Guests for Conan|date=2010-10-21|accessdate=2010-10-21|publisher=Turner Newsroom|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101024190557/http://news.turner.com/article_display.cfm?article_id=5425|archive-date=2010-10-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。演员[[乔恩·哈姆|乔恩·哈姆]]以[[AMC|AMC]]电视剧[[广告狂人|广告狂人]]角色唐·德雷珀登场。[[CNN|CNN]]脱口秀节目《[[拉里金现场|拉里金现场]]》主持人[[拉里·金|拉里·金]]作冷场演出。喜剧演员[[里奇·格威斯|里奇·格威斯]]向柯南传递了他对新节目的祝福（事先消音），然而为日后的失业表示哀悼<ref name="timefirst"/>。

首播获得电视评论家积极评价，“是档宽松且更诡异的深夜脱口秀节目，但终究是深夜脱口秀<ref name="timefirst"/>。”《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》的詹姆斯·波尼沃兹称节目让人愉快，还拿它跟奥布莱恩时期的《深夜秀》作比较。但他而后表示，“带来的信息，总体上......是《柯南秀》并未完全展示脱口秀节目形式的再创造。他做的是一档被NBC封杀的深夜脱口秀节目。”他赞扬了开头独白及柯南与杰克·怀特在结尾处的表现<ref name="timefirst"/>。[[美联社|美联社]]的弗雷泽·摩尔称节目“时髦地继承柯南主持《今夜秀》时来之不易的经验教训”，承认奥布莱恩在节目中的表现“辛辣得舒服<ref name="washap">{{cite news |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2010/11/09/AR2010110900862.html?tid=obinsite |title=Conan O'Brien returns to late-night TV with ease |publisher=The Washington Post |agency=Associated Press |last=Moore |first=Frazier |accessdate=2010-11-09 |date=2010-11-09 }}{{Dead link}}</ref>”。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的肯·塔克赞赏手淫熊的客串，从而称节目“令人愉快，给人留下点深刻印象<ref name="ewfirst">{{cite web |url=http://watching-tv.ew.com/2010/11/09/conan-obrien-review/ |title='Conan' first-night review: Coco's so-so show |first=Ken |last=Tucker |publisher=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2010-11-09 |date=2010-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101110211812/http://watching-tv.ew.com/2010/11/09/conan-obrien-review/ |archive-date=2010-11-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>”。但《[[人物_(杂志)|人物]]》的汤姆·盖里托指责节目“谦虚、低调而略显尴尬<ref name="peoplefirst">{{cite web |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20440527,00.html |title=People's TV Critic Picks Conan's Top 3 Moments |publisher=人物杂志 |accessdate=2010-11-09 |date=2010-11-09 |last=Gliatto |first=Tom |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101112003543/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20440527,00.html |archive-date=2010-11-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>”。

